          "type": "PQ"
        },
        {
          "id": "2deb41ddf67a_22",
          "href": null,
          "name": "93a2",
          "text": "We need a more holistic understanding of economics to inform a fundamental redesign of our economic and monetary systems at local, regional and global scales. We need to co-create a collaborative economics of human solidarity that is regenerative and operates safely within planetary boundaries. The new story underlying the re-design of our economic system has to recognize our fundamental interdependence in a reality were either all of humanity and life as a whole “wins” or in the long run nobody will win. As a general introduction to this dimension you may wish to watch one of the following videos:",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
